    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small knives comprising a blade mounted on a pivot, often having a saddle for a finger-rest. Such knives are used most often in leatherworking, but also in other occupations, including historically in surgery.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
